# ABOUTME: Ollama Modelfile for the Handy dictation post-processing model.
# ABOUTME: qwen3.5:4b made deterministic and length-bounded; build with:
# ABOUTME:   ollama create handy-qwen -f handy-qwen.Modelfile   (then point Handy at "handy-qwen")
FROM qwen3.5:4b

# Deterministic output for a mechanical transform (no sampling drift / spurious punctuation).
PARAMETER temperature 0
PARAMETER top_p 1

# Hard cap so a degenerate generation can never hang the dictation UI (we hit a 9-minute
# unbounded run during testing). 512 covers any realistic dictation; raise if you dictate
# very long passages. NOTE: if Handy sends its own max_tokens, that overrides this default.
PARAMETER num_predict 512